<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <link rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-icons/1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" />

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/frontend/main.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/frontend/about/about.css">
  <title>Kick Pulse About</title>
</head>

<body class="mb-5">
  <%- include('./components/preloader') %>
  <%- include('./components/search-modal') %>

  <div class="content">
    <%- include('./components/header') %>
    <main class="container-fluid mb-5">
      <section class="container py-5">
        <div class="row mb-4">
          <div class="col text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">About Kick Pulse</h1>
            <p class="lead">Kick Pulse is a premier sneaker retailer dedicated to bringing you the latest and greatest footwear from top brands like Adidas, Nike, Converse, Vans, and more.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Our Story</h2>
            <p>With a passion for sneakers and a commitment to quality, we offer a diverse selection that caters to sneaker enthusiasts and casual shoppers alike. We proudly operate five strategically located stores across the country, providing a convenient and welcoming shopping experience.</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Miami</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-primary me-2"></i>New York</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Los Angeles</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Seattle</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Each store is designed to help you find the perfect pair of sneakers with personalized service and a vast selection.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <img src="../photos/sneakersfull.webp" alt="About Us Image" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm">
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our platform extends this convenience online, offering detailed product descriptions, high-quality images, fast shipping, and hassle-free returns. At Kick Pulse, our mission is to connect you with the sneakers you love while delivering exceptional service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Wide range of high-quality shoes</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Latest fashion trends</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Exceptional customer service</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Competitive prices</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-primary me-2"></i>Easy returns and exchanges</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    
    <%- include('./components/footer') %>

  </div>


  <!-- MODALS -->
  <%- include('./components/cart-modal') %>
  <%- include('./components/quickview-modal') %>
  <% if(!session.userId) { %>
  <%- include('./components/register-modal') %>
  <%- include('./components/login-modal') %>
  <% } %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script type="module" src="/frontend/about/about.js"></script>
</body>

</html>